'''西部男孩'''（West Side Boys）是[[塞拉利昂|塞拉利昂]]的一个武装团体<ref name="Sherwell">{{Cite news|author=Sherwell|first=Philip|date=3 September 2000|title=Caught with their guard down|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/sierraleone/1353972/Caught-with-their-guard-down.html|work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]|accessdate=18 September 2015|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914103126/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/sierraleone/1353972/Caught-with-their-guard-down.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。西部男孩在一定程度上受到美国[[嘻哈音樂|说唱]]和帮派说唱音乐的影响<ref>{{Citation|last=Reno|first=William|publication-date=February 2003|title=Political Networks in a Failing State The Roots and Future of Violent Conflict in Sierra Leone|publisher=Internationale Politik und Gesellschaft, International Politics and Society|url=http://www.usaid.gov/sl/sl_new/news/2004/040531_atunda_ayenda/index.htm|access-date=2008-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723215930/http://www.usaid.gov/sl/sl_new/news/2004/040531_atunda_ayenda/index.htm|archivedate=2008-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>Fofana, Lansana [http://www.ipsnews.net/1998/10/sierra-leone-rap-stars-t-shirt-a-major-factor-in-conflict/ "SIERRA LEONE: Rap Star’s T-shirt A Major Factor In Conflict"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ipsnews.net/1998/10/sierra-leone-rap-stars-t-shirt-a-major-factor-in-conflict/ |date=20200914103134 }}, ''Inter Press Service'', October, 1998, retrieved 20 May 2018.</ref>。

他们曾抓获并扣留了{{link-en|联合国塞拉利昂特派团|United Nations Mission in Sierra Leone}}的维持和平人员，并于2000年8月抓获了一支由[[皇家愛爾蘭團|英国皇家爱尔兰团]]士兵组成的巡逻队及其{{link-en|塞拉利昂军队|Sierra Leone Army}}联络官。后来在2000年9月的[[巴拉斯行动|巴拉斯行动]]期间，西部男孩在[[特种空勤团|特种空勤团]]和{{link-en|伞兵团|Parachute Regiment}}的一次行动中被消灭。在西部男孩被摧毁之前，该組織的规模已扩大到600人左右<ref name="Sherwell" />。

